      "rootCause": "Backend user-create failed after a successful client signup (\"create user -> 500: {\\\"error\\\":\\\"Unknown Error. Try Again\\\"}\"). The Firebase Admin SDK cannot mint an OAuth token (\"invalid_grant: Invalid JWT Signature\"): the service-account key in FIREBASE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_JSON is revoked/incorrect, or the host clock is skewed (this machine reports 2026).",
